      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an uncompromising standard that warrants the designation of showroom condition. The exterior retains its original luster, free of imperfections, while the interior remains in a state of pristine preservation. This vehicle has been curated for the most discerning enthusiast, offering a mechanical and aesthetic experience that is indistinguishable from its initial delivery. We invite rigorous inspection to confirm its peerless status.",
