    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of naturally aspirated precision, featuring the iconic S54 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a fully serviced Double-VANOS system. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis is structurally immaculate, with critical rear subframe mounting points inspected and verified for total integrity. Every bushing and suspension component retains factory-spec compliance, while the braking system utilizes cross-drilled rotors for consistent thermal management. This is a collector-grade vehicle with zero deferred maintenance, offering a pure, analog driving experience in a condition that mirrors its original delivery.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
